==Chinese==
===Phrase===
[[Simplified Chinese]]: 一枝草，一点露
[[Traditional Chinese]]: 一枝草，一點露
[[Pinyin]]: yī zhī căo, yī dĭan lù
# {{idiom}} As long as one is still breathing, one has a chance to live.
# {{idiom}} There is always a way out.
===Etymology===
Literally: For every blade of grass, there is a drop of dew.
